Proxmark3
• Device used to analyze RFID and NFC cards.
• Threat: Can expose card cloning and access control weaknesses.
• Ethical Use: Used to test physical security and smart card protection systems.

Malicious Keyboard
• Modified keyboard capable of recording or injecting keystrokes.
• Threat: Can capture login credentials and sensitive data.
• Ethical Use: Used to test hardware tampering risks and endpoint security.
